    • it.polimi.automata.io.ba.transformers.HyperMetadataToTransitionTransformer<LABEL,TRANSITION,TRANSITIONFACTORY>
  • Type Parameters:
    LABEL - is the type of the Label which is applied to the transitions of the Buchi Automaton which must implement the interface Label
    TRANSITION - is the type of the transitions of the automaton. It must implement the interface Transition
    TRANSITIONFACTORY - is the factory which allows to create the transitions. It must implement the interface TransitionFactory
